attributes.name: Black Mamba 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: Black Mamba is an indica-dominant hybrid strain known for its dark, dense buds and potent effects. It often has a sweet and earthy aroma with hints of spice. Black Mamba delivers a strong, long-lasting high, inducing deep relaxation, sedation, and a dreamy, introspective state.

attributes.name: Blueberry Dream 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: Blueberry Dream is a hybrid strain that combines the genetics of Blueberryand Haze strains. It typically has a sweet and fruity aroma with hints of blueberry. This strain offers a balanced high, providing both a relaxed body sensation and a euphoric cerebral effect.

attributes.name: Ghost Train Haze 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: Ghost Train Haze is a potent sativa-dominant strain known for its high THC content. It often has a citrusy aroma with hints of floral and spice. Ghost Train Haze produces a strong cerebral high, characterized by intense euphoria, creativity, and an uplifting, energizing effect.

attributes.name: Guava 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: Guava is a sativa-dominant hybrid strain that typically has a tropical and fruity aroma with notes of guava. It offers a relaxing and calming high, promoting deep physical relaxation, stress relief, and potential pain management. Guava is known for its pleasant flavor and potential mood elevation.

attributes.name: White Fire OG 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: White Fire OG, also known as WiFi OG, is a hybrid strain that combines the genetics of Fire OG and The White. It generally has a pungent, diesel-like aroma with earthy undertones. White Fire OG provides a powerful and uplifting cerebral high along with deep relaxation and potential pain relief.

attributes.name: Apple Jacks 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: Apple Jacks is a sativa strain that combines the genetics of Jack Herer and White Widow. It usually has a sweet and fruity aroma with hints of apple and citrus. Apple Jacks provides a stimulating and energetic high, promoting mental clarity, focus, and a sense of happiness.

attributes.name: GMO 2g All-In-One Vape
attributes.body: GMO, short for Garlic, Mushroom, and Onion, is an indica-dominant hybrid strain with a distinct and pungent aroma reminiscent of its name. It typically offers a combination of savory and earthy flavors. GMO is known for its potent effects, including deep relaxation, euphoria, and potential appetite stimulation.

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Concord Cream
attributes.body: Concord Cream, a predominantly Indica strain, is the sweet sweet love child of Grape Bubba and Cookies & Cream. This soothing bud, rich in flavor, is a must-try for any grape strain fans. True to its name, Concord Cream boasts a super sweet and creamy fruity grape flavor complemented by notes of flowery violet and vanilla. The aroma mirrors this profile with a hint of sour grapefruit. Concord Cream is a favored choice for addressing various conditions across a whole spectrum, including stress, anxiety, muscle spasms, cramps, depression, and insomnia. The Concord Cream high unfolds gradually, initiating with a slow burn of euphoria that melts the mad/sad away. Concord Cream is wonderful for consumers that have social anxiety as its a very talkative, giggly strain! As the mental boost persists, a sense of physical relaxation takes over, eventually inducing a sleepy, sedative state.

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Donny Burger
attributes.body: Indulge your palate with Donny Burger, a robust indica strain crafted from the combination of GMO and Han Solo Burger. Boasting a multifaceted earthy fragrance that captivates, Donny Burger delivers a calming and euphoric experience. Its gentle physical sensation eases the body into a subtle state of relaxation, making this potent flower a beneficial choice for addressing conditions like anxiety, chronic pain, depression, and inflammation. Donny Burger from Enchanted Botanicals is also the winner of 3rd place in the High Times Cannabis Cup Indica Category!

attributes.name: Enchanted Botanicals - Modified Grapes
attributes.body: Modified Grapes is an Indica weed strain resulting from a cross between GMO and Purple Punch. This strain is favored by experienced cannabis consumers for its beautiful purple color and its flavors reminiscent of grape, berry, and honey. According to our customers, Modified Grapes is associated with effects like drowsiness, relaxation, and arousal. Consumers often turn to Modified Grapes to alleviate symptoms related to anxiety, stress, and insomnia.

attributes.name: RSO | Syringe
attributes.body: What is RSO? Put simply, RSO is an oil derived from cannabis. But rather than a solvent extract that strips trichomes from buds, RSO contains all the cannabinoids, terpenes, and additional compounds of the whole cannabis plant. The extraction process is complex and fairly long, similar to making a tincture. It’s typically near-black in color, and, admittedly, doesn’t taste great due to its high amount of plant matter (it uses the whole plant). RSO was created as a medicinal therapeutic for cancer and other chronic health conditions, like MS and asthma. While Rick Simpson no longer produces the oil himself, it remains a crucial ingredient in the treatment plans of patients across North America.

attributes.name: Strawberry Stardawg | Live Badder
attributes.body: Pharmers Quality Concentrates is New Mexico’s premier manufacture of high-end concentrates. We are the chemistry focused cannabis extraction laboratory in Socorro, New Mexico. We strive to provide the highest quality cannabis oil available by imploring the use of modern organic chemistry. We specialize in cannabinoid extraction, distillation, isolation, and remediation of contaminants. We believe it is important to trust the source of your medicine. Along time ago before marijuana prohibition, people were able to purchase Cannabis Oil at Pharmacies across the country. These pharmacies sold classily, trusted brands of medicine made by chemists with a true want to help and provide relief to their consumers. These brands were proud and stood by their medicine and so do we. Our motto is QUALITY COMES STANDARD because we believe it should! Our highly qualified staff of Laboratory Technicians will ensure that the utmost care is taken in the handling, extraction, and processing of your Cannabis oils. Selection of quality biomass is key to obtaining the best tasting and greater yielding concentrates. Let us work with your company to provide your patients with the best medication in New Mexico.

attributes.name: Artisan Green Chile Gummies
attributes.body: ORALE gummies are crafted in small batches to preserve the authentic taste of New Mexico’s favorite chiles. The flavor of ORALE Green Chile Gummies is just as unique as New Mexico itself. The ORALE Green Chile Gummy is prized for its lightly pungent, bright & sweet taste with a hot & spicy finish. Also try ORALE Green Chili Gummies, or try them Christmas Style (both together!). Made with the finest New Mexican Hatch chilies, our gummies are vegan, all natural and blended with our high-quality potent cannabis. Consume orally and wait 1 hour for full effect. Keep out of reach of children and animals. Each bag contains 10- 10 mg THC gummies (100 mg Total THC)

Prohibition 37 flower is our specialty and what we have built our brand on. Our production facilities include 2 state-of-the-art indoor cultivations totaling 14,000 sq ft in our home city of Albuquerque. We also have an outdoor farm in Belen, and greenhouse productions in Belen and Gallup. Our mission is to destigmatize the industry, produce outstanding quality cannabis, and positively contribute to the quality of life of our patients and customers. We currently grow over 75 cultivars, and are continually adding the newest and most sought after genetics to bring to every corner of New Mexico. WHO IS P37? Prohibition 37 is a physician-led, nationally recognized, and award-winning vertical cannabis company. P37 is highly focused on the customer experience and science of the medicinal and recreational effects of its many products. Our name is derived from The Marihuana Tax Act of 1937, which was a U.S. federal law that effectively criminalized the possession and distribution of marijuana. While it did not directly ban the cannabis plant, it imposed strict regulations and heavy taxes on its cultivation, sales, and use. This made it impossible to legally engage in these activities, leading to a de facto prohibition of cannabis. The Act played a significant role in shaping the modern approach to marijuana regulation in the United States.\ SOCIAL EQUITY AND JUSTICE The Marihuana Tax Act of 1937 disproportionately targeted minorities, particularly African, Mexican, and Jewish American communities. While the act did not explicitly mention racial or ethnic groups, its implementation and enforcement were marked by tremendous racial bias and discrimination. Law enforcement, for example, selectively targeted and arrested individuals from minority groups and used marijuana-related offenses as a pretext for discriminatory actions. This contributed to the disproportionate impact of the Act on minorities, perpetuating racial stereotypes and injustices for generations to come. Our mission at Prohibition 37 is to reverse decades of cannabis-related injustice and create a healthy, communal, and scientific approach to cannabis use.

attributes.name: Frenchy Pebbles | Disposable
attributes.body: Live Extraction As opposed to drying and curing, the essence of the living cannabis plant is preserved through freezing immediately after harvest and remaining frozen throughout extraction. This process retains a broader spectrum of live terpenes and cannabinoids in higher volumes, yielding an exotic alternative to traditional BHO extracts. Live BHO typically resembles that of the plant in its final stage of flowering when terpene potency is at its peak generating robust aromatics and delivering unmatched piquancy. Adding enticing nuances to the typical cannabis extract palate, live extracts have become the first choice of the modern connoisseur. Traditional Extraction Utilizing dried and cured cannabis, this process extracts the cannabinoids, along with the aroma and flavor of the plant you love into a powerful concentrate. The best extracts of cannabis leave behind many of the carcinogenic substances the plants produce while preserving the desirable contents they contain. Cannabis extract can manifest a variety of dynamic textures, consistencies, and useful by-products such as H.T.S.F.E. Furthermore, cannabis extract has become the industry’s preferred method for infusing activated cannabinoids, such as ?9-THC, into ingestible and topical products. Refined Extraction Take into consideration the environmental pollutants and agricultural contaminants that can be associated with cannabis cultivation, the subsequent extracts can contain unwanted impurities, pigments, and even harmful chemicals. Our proprietary filtration techniques and chromatography methodologies allow us to remediate compromised or otherwise undesirable extracts while maintaining the desirable components such as cannabinoids and terpenes. The end result meets all standards for consumption from shelf-ready solid extract to liquid and food-grade variations. By making these processes available, we aim to help eliminate large-scale waste associated with the ever-expanding industry of commercial cannabis.

attributes.name: Dream Berry | Fast Asleep Gummies
attributes.body: Feel sleepy in just 5-15 minutes... with no next-day grogginess. These revolutionary nighttime gummies deliver a sweet mixed berry flavor, along with a custom blend of CBD, THC, CBG, CBN, and melatonin. They’re also enhanced with more than 30 specialized terpenes, curated based on AI-generated data from thousands of consumer experiences — and all delivered via fast-acting molecular encapsulation technology. What Makes Us Wana? Excellence. We've never been satisfied with "good enough," not even when we were just a scrappy Boulder-based start-up trying to make our way in a newly legalized industry. When many companies cut corners, using inferior ingredients like animal-derived gelatin and artificial sweeteners, we crafted a vegan, terpene-enhanced, melt-proof recipe that virtually any adult could enjoy. While our competitors waited for state regulations to require testing, we tested our products for potency and consistency from the start. And now, more than a decade later, customers all over the U.S. and Canada trust us to deliver a premium cannabis experience, every time they reach for a Wana product.

attributes.name: Red Pepper | Phuse Blunt
attributes.body: Crafted to pay homage to the old fashioned blunt. Each PhuseWoods Oiler features a 9mm Lock & Load glass filter tip for an exceptionally smooth draw. Rolled by hand in a High Hemp Organic Wrap encasing 2g of whole flower cannabis, coated in 0.25g of Pharmers' select distillate, and finally dusted in 0.25g of top shelf kief for a 3rd dimension of potency and flavor. To cater to diverse tastes, PhuseWoods Oilers come in an array of flavors – Cream, Grape, Cherry, and Natural – providing an opportunity to explore a spectrum of inphused flavors with a kick only PHUSE products can offer.
